      <title>保时捷交付量因中国市场需求减弱和车型变化而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/porsche-deliveries-fall-on-weaker-demand-in-china-model-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于德国汽车制造商推出了多款新车型且中国市场需求进一步疲软，保时捷汽车公司 (Porsche AG) 上半年交付量下降了 7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/porsche-deliveries-fall-on-weaker-demand-in-china-model-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
